### -------------------------------------------------------
### Frontend Discovery Service — Admin API
### -------------------------------------------------------
### Prerequisites:
###   1. Fill Cognito + API values in .env.local
###   2. Run `pnpm get-token` to fetch and store a token
### -------------------------------------------------------

### Set these before running version/deployment requests:
@mfeId = PASTE_MFE_ID
@commitSha = PASTE_COMMIT_SHA
@cdnBase = https://your-cdn.cloudfront.net


### =====================
### Micro Frontends
### =====================

### List MFEs in staging project
GET {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_ADMIN_API}}/projects/{{$dotenv STAGING_PROJECT_ID}}/microFrontends
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_TOKEN}}

###

### List MFEs in production project
GET {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_ADMIN_API}}/projects/{{$dotenv PRODUCTION_PROJECT_ID}}/microFrontends
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_TOKEN}}

###

### Create a new MFE in staging
# POST {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_ADMIN_API}}/projects/{{$dotenv STAGING_PROJECT_ID}}/microFrontends
# Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_TOKEN}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "microFrontend": {
#     "name": "shop"
#   }
# }


### =====================
### Versions
### =====================

### List all versions for an MFE
GET {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_ADMIN_API}}/projects/{{$dotenv STAGING_PROJECT_ID}}/microFrontends/{{mfeId}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_TOKEN}}

###

### Register a new version (first version — no deployment strategy)
POST {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_ADMIN_API}}/projects/{{$dotenv STAGING_PROJECT_ID}}/microFrontends/{{mfeId}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "version": {
    "url": "{{cdnBase}}/shop/{{commitSha}}/remoteEntry.js",
    "metadata": {
      "version": "{{commitSha}}",
      "integrity": "sha384-..."
    }
  }
}

###

### Register version with deployment strategy (subsequent versions)
POST {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_ADMIN_API}}/projects/{{$dotenv STAGING_PROJECT_ID}}/microFrontends/{{mfeId}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "version": {
    "url": "{{cdnBase}}/shop/{{commitSha}}/remoteEntry.js",
    "metadata": {
      "version": "{{commitSha}}",
      "integrity": "sha384-..."
    }
  },
  "deploymentStrategy": "AllAtOnce"
}


### =====================
### Deployments (Promote)
### =====================

### Promote a version to production (AllAtOnce)
POST {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_ADMIN_API}}/projects/{{$dotenv PRODUCTION_PROJECT_ID}}/microFrontends/{{mfeId}}/deployment
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetVersion": "{{commitSha}}",
  "deploymentStrategy": "AllAtOnce"
}

###

### Promote with Linear (gradual rollout)
# POST {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_ADMIN_API}}/projects/{{$dotenv PRODUCTION_PROJECT_ID}}/microFrontends/{{mfeId}}/deployment
# Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_TOKEN}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "targetVersion": "{{commitSha}}",
#   "deploymentStrategy": "Linear"
# }

###

### Promote with Canary
# POST {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_ADMIN_API}}/projects/{{$dotenv PRODUCTION_PROJECT_ID}}/microFrontends/{{mfeId}}/deployment
# Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv DISCOVERY_TOKEN}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "targetVersion": "{{commitSha}}",
#   "deploymentStrategy": "Canary"
# }
